So let's first do full introductions.

12
00:00:36,554 --> 00:00:37,735
My name is Jan-Bert van Beek.

13
00:00:37,735 --> 00:00:40,178
I am the studio art director and animation art director

14
00:00:40,178 --> 00:00:41,700
at Guerrilla Games.

15
00:00:41,700 --> 00:00:43,742
And as you may know, Guerrilla Games

16
00:00:43,742 --> 00:00:46,045
is part of Sony Worldwide Studios.

17
00:00:46,045 --> 00:00:49,689
So that's a group of 14 very, very different game developers

18
00:00:49,689 --> 00:00:52,333
from Naughty Dog, Guerrilla, Media Molecule, Polyphony.

19
00:00:53,453 --> 00:00:56,654
that all work together to make the first party portfolio of Sony.

20
00:00:56,654 --> 00:01:01,795
Now, we ourselves are Guerrilla, we're based in Amsterdam, lovely city.

21
00:01:01,795 --> 00:01:05,536
And as you may know, the last title that we did was Horizon Zero Dawn,

22
00:01:05,536 --> 00:01:09,517
which was also our first open world action role-playing game.

23
00:01:09,517 --> 00:01:11,837
So just to get an idea, who has played Horizon?

24
00:01:11,837 --> 00:01:15,118
Very good. Who has finished Horizon?

