00:38:22,325 --> 00:38:33,790
So there's this movement or they're making this philosophy in industrial design which

712
00:38:33,790 --> 00:38:39,512
they call biomimetic design. And it's an industrial design philosophy that carefully looks at

713
00:38:39,512 --> 00:38:41,833
nature to solve certain engineering issues.

714
00:38:42,443 --> 00:38:44,303
So the notion behind this philosophy

715
00:38:44,303 --> 00:38:47,004
is that if you have millions and millions and millions

716
00:38:47,004 --> 00:38:49,325
of years of evolution, the solutions that

717
00:38:49,325 --> 00:38:51,706
tend to come out of that are very highly efficient

718
00:38:51,706 --> 00:38:53,267
solutions.

719
00:38:53,267 --> 00:38:55,387
A famous example of this biomedic design

720
00:38:55,387 --> 00:38:57,328
is a problem that Japanese engineers

721
00:38:57,328 --> 00:39:00,509
had when they tried to solve the famous bullet trains.

722
00:39:00,509 --> 00:39:02,230
Now, when they first made these things,

723
00:39:02,230 --> 00:39:04,230
they would send them into tunnels.

724
00:39:04,230 --> 00:39:05,831
And the moment that they hit the tunnel, there

725
00:39:05,831 --> 00:39:07,831
would be these air pressure events which literally

726
00:39:07,831 --> 00:39:10,132
ripped the whole train apart.

727
00:39:10,132 --> 00:39:11,753
And that's bad for passengers.

728
00:39:13,044 --> 00:39:14,924
So they were looking for a solution,

729
00:39:14,924 --> 00:39:17,406
and they got their inspiration from the beak

730
00:39:17,406 --> 00:39:18,947
shape of the kingfisher.

731
00:39:18,947 --> 00:39:20,708
Because this is a bird that, once it

732
00:39:20,708 --> 00:39:24,209
hits the water to catch a fish, it almost makes no splash.

733
00:39:24,209 --> 00:39:26,871
So this is a perfect sort of evolution

734
00:39:26,871 --> 00:39:30,232
that created the shape, the most efficient form

735
00:39:30,232 --> 00:39:31,733
of hydrodynamics.

736
00:39:31,733 --> 00:39:33,914
And once they took that shape and put it

737
00:39:33,914 --> 00:39:36,576
on top of these trains, the trains didn't fall apart.

738
00:39:36,576 --> 00:39:37,977
And people were happy.

